Component: Correctness of adding an item to the cart

Precondition: Go to https://www.ozon.ru/

Steps
1. Enter the required product in the search bar (Bicycles OLESYANEL)
2. Click on a product
3. Choose the right size (44)
4. Select the state of the goods "New"
5. Press the button "Add to cart"
5. Select the quantity of goods (1 pc.)
6. Go to the cart (cart icon in the upper right corner)
7. We see the amount of 399 rubles.

Expected Result
OLESYANEL cycling shorts (size 44; "New" condition; price: 399 rub) were added to the cart in the amount of 1 pc. and the total amount of the order was 399 rub.

*Next to the Cart icon, the number of items in the cart icon has been added/changed.
